docs.lead_paragraph: NEW-YORK. "B." -- She is still living. BROOKLYN. Mrs. Mary E. Rankin of 58 Division Avenue, Brooklyn, began a suit yesterday for an absolute divorce from Albert Rankin, and at the same time instituted an action to recover $100,000 damages from Miss Mary Bothwick of 546 East One Hundred and Sixty-fifth Street, NewYork, for alienating Mr. Rankin's affections.
